{"tid":18033,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"縱橫遊呢間公司真係垃圾","createTime":"2016-12-02T05:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-12T01:07:02.000Z","uid":6702,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0bd70eddcddc33991c422d52bb8acfe3dcfad43b","tid":18033,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:24:09.000Z","msg":"老闆又度縮&hellip;同事又閪&hellip;個撚個篤灰狗&hellip;你地自己做飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c402dd9d44c831984de30ac29c2b07c0eaf1b22","tid":18033,"uid":33359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:24:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>老闆又度縮&hellip;同事又閪&hellip;個撚個篤灰狗&hellip;你地自己做飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMore"},{"pid":"10fda798ecd9a70285d9ee9df8cdb490612190af","tid":18033,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T05:41:54.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>老闆又度縮&hellip;同事又閪&hellip;個撚個篤灰狗&hellip;你地自己做飽佢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nMore</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n個老細出啲offer永遠差過出面&hellip;跟住又會問啲leader比意見睇下點請人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n老細旺季唔肯做group ticket&hellip;驚會蝕喎&hellip;做過呢行都知旺季大部同行都係靠group ticket做生意啦&hellip;呢條友都唔知諗乜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最on9嘅係返call centre 要着整齊制服&hellip;但制服全部都係自費&hellip;<br />\n老細為左迎合市場需求&hellip;強推網上訂購&hellip;但試都未試過就推出街&hellip;結果咪多bugs又要同事跟&hellip;試過有單個客上網買business 點知班機都無business 結果咪要賠錢比個客<br />\n有個同事試過食飯睇劇&hellip;結果比人篤灰&hellip;公司就炒佢&hellip;事後原來係公司覺得佢人工高要炒佢&hellip;而家炒下炒下唔夠人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申&hellip;9up下嫁咋<span style=\"font-size: x-small;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">戴定頭盔先</span></span>"},{"pid":"a9524332cc5e7230dc908b58c9b0a97ef71e38e8","tid":18033,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T06:00:43.000Z","msg":"仲有樣就係老細要我地2個星期上一次服務堂&hellip;好似話用左幾十萬定十幾萬請佢返黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 但我問過做得耐個啲同事.&hellip;乜成日比人投訴服務態度差咩？佢又話唔係&hellip;最常投訴係唔成團但同事講錯成團呢啲case<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 咁個堂上黎做咩&hellip;老細話要就要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a72265d0d608eff0749e42779281f8c05c8dcaa5","tid":18033,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:42:27.000Z","msg":"認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56d022427abf99ec86a05e28932a67a31e32bd3d","tid":18033,"uid":18377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:44:20.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一時又話9up<br />\n依家又話認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"099c9aa26e08888b8bf0340b1a37909585f87f2d","tid":18033,"uid":35746,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:47:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ff0c3d7d3c13fa63c9581765aeddec5f004c37c","tid":18033,"uid":6702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-02T08:47:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>認真po無人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你一時又話9up<br />\n依家又話認真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n戴下頭盔姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0509ef5a463aca45c0cdce4ae96667673304b411","tid":18033,"uid":30272,"l